00:18:32,890 --> 00:18:34,890
I, entrusted by the plaintiff of the case,

393
00:18:34,890 --> 00:18:37,640
act as agent ad litem of Zhang, Li, Yang,

394
00:18:37,770 --> 00:18:40,770
Zhao, Du and Jiang,

