519
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,050
And it’s not yours.

520
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:08,090
It’s removed from my arm.

521
00:24:08,090 --> 00:24:08,850
It’s not yours, either.

522
00:24:08,850 --> 00:24:09,330
Besides,

523
00:24:09,330 --> 00:24:10,130
